Interface RichObjectWrapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ObjectWrapper, ObjectWrapperAndUnwrapper, ObjectWrapperWithAPISupport
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultObjectWrapper, RestrictedObjectWrapper

    public interface RichObjectWrapper
extends ObjectWrapperAndUnwrapper, ObjectWrapperWithAPISupport
    Experimental - subject to change: Union of the interfaces that a typical feature rich ObjectWrapper is expected to implement.

    Experimental status warning: This interface is subject to change on non-backward compatible ways, hence, it shouldn't be implemented outside FreeMarker yet.
